Change Log (2025-12-05)
Updated summarization logic

For each section: extract → summarize → check rules
Store outputs

Section Loop Logic (Updated)
Variables
section → current section being processed

summary_level → controls the style of summary output

Allowed values: "short", "detailed"

Loop Steps
Iterate through each section in the document.

Extract the section title and content.

Apply summarization logic based on summary_level:

Case A: summary_level = "short"

Generate a compact summary of the section in 1–2 sentences.

Do not include bullet points.

Case B: summary_level = "detailed"

Generate a short paragraph summary of the section.

Additionally, produce a bullet list of 3–5 key points highlighting the most important details.

Output the summary for the section in the required format.

Proceed to the next section until all sections are processed.
